ShapePointStore, VertexStore
public abstract class NodeStore<T extends GraphNode> extends ArchivedGraphElementStore<T>
Store of node information for subclasses of GraphNode, including Vertex and ShapePoint. This store holds node identifiers and node locations and maps from node identifiers to indexes.

In addition, this store holds all node information when a Graph supports it, as determined by Graph.supportsFullPbfNodeInformation(). Full node information is only a requirement for map editing tools used by the OpenTerra team, such as the map-enhancer project, also known as Cygnus. Having full node information is required in order to contribute enhanced or fixed map data back to the OSM community. In cases where full node information is being stored like this, node information for all the nodes in each edge's road shape will be stored in the ShapePointStore subclass of this class.
